      "disable": "<p>@Check[type:thievery|dc:31] (expert) to disconnect each tiger head from the wall or @Check[type:perception|dc:29] to notice the bypass switch at the entrance of the room</p>",
      "description": "<p>The tiger heads on the walls of the chamber animate and viciously attack anyone within reach.</p>",
      "reset": "<p>The trap deactivates and resets if there are no creatures present in the room or once the bypass switch is flipped.</p>",
      "routine": "<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">T</span> The trap uses each action to make a bite Strike against a creature within reach. Only one action may be used per tiger head, to a maximum of three heads each round.</p>"
